{"tid":2172954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共頻叫囂武統 南北連續實彈軍演…法媒一圖踢爆","createTime":"2020-08-25T03:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T03:17:25.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1c9566e5e0c95fa606a7203d9755faa025372eaa","tid":2172954,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T03:16:28.000Z","msg":"中國共軍東部戰區13日表示，解放軍東部戰區以多軍種多方向成體系出動兵力，將在台灣海峽及南北兩端「連續組織實戰化演練」，恫嚇台灣意圖明顯。對此，法國媒體曝光中國軍演真實位置，從圖片上面來看，竟然離台灣還有「一大段距離」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s-yimg-com.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w820/s/s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/KRMR.CmHwuFy6Gkx591evQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM2MA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/FizkfuuxchuUnFXdKDbLmg--~B/aD00NTA7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/setn.com.tw/932bb0727c4d21dfddda598b7aac593d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-yimg-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw820%2Fs%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FKRMR.CmHwuFy6Gkx591evQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FFizkfuuxchuUnFXdKDbLmg--~B%2FaD00NTA7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F932bb0727c4d21dfddda598b7aac593d&h=a1dea110&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法國媒體曝光中國軍演真實位置。（圖／翻攝自法國媒體《East Pendulum》推特）<br />\n<br />\n據中國媒體報導，中國解放軍東部戰區發言人張春暉13日下午稱，東部戰區多軍種在多方向成體系出動兵力，在台灣海峽及南北兩端連續組織實戰化演練，進一步檢驗提升多軍種聯合作戰能力。張春暉更火大開嗆，「個別大國」在台灣問題上消極動向不斷，向台獨勢力發出嚴重錯誤信號，嚴重威脅台海地區和平與穩定。<br />\n<br />\n不過根據法國媒體《East Pendulum》23日推特的軍演位置圖片顯示，大陸在台海南北演習，離台灣還有「一大段距離」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E9%A0%BB%E5%8F%AB%E5%9B%82%E6%AD%A6%E7%B5%B1%E8%BB%8D%E6%BC%94-%E6%B3%95%E5%AA%92-%E5%9C%96%E7%8B%A0%E6%89%93%E8%87%89-024532018.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E9%25A0%25BB%25E5%258F%25AB%25E5%259B%2582%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%25BC%2594-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E5%259C%2596%25E7%258B%25A0%25E6%2589%2593%25E8%2587%2589-024532018.html&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3Sble0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=fdcfab14\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E9%A0%BB%E5%8F%AB%E5%9B%82%E6%AD%A6%E7%B5%B1%E8%BB%8D%E6%BC%94-%E6%B3%95%E5%AA%92-%E5%9C%96%E7%8B%A0%E6%89%93%E8%87%89-024532018.html</a>"},{"pid":"b3642c969bb5f44ecd61d43b31833665ae8774f8","tid":2172954,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T03:17:25.000Z","msg":"張春暉 南華之前個龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}